  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Insomnia can be a chronic problem that leads to significant daytime fatigue, stress and
      numerous negative health consequences including depression. Advanced Medical Electronics, in
      partnership with researchers are the University of Pennsylvania, propose developing an
      innovative, non-drug, low-risk, intervention that can be implemented on mobile devices for
      the treatment of insomnia
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
